data.text:
2003

1 hr 46 mins

Drama, Comedy

PG13

Watchlist

Where to Watch

Singer Charlotte Church makes her big-screen debut in this wonderfully off-kilter romantic comedy. Director and co-writer Craig Ferguson stars as an aging, troubled former pop star who discovers he has a teenage daughter (Church), who also has a talent for singing. Jemma Redgrave, Joss Ackland.
